{"tid":2116324,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「學術研究」易傳染程度：小巴？巴士？的士？","createTime":"2020-07-20T05:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T13:19:14.000Z","uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb77ad535a694a9105c7ae6151ec00f6b75f9a3","tid":2116324,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"連登有無人有興趣研究下，<br />\nQ1. 究竟武漢肺炎會唔會係小巴/巴士/的士傳染？<br />\nQ2. 如果會，會係邊到最易中？<br />\n<br />\n到最近有好多單案搵唔到源頭。<br />\n已經有唔止一單案例講緊正常人會係短時間內同病患者接觸（傾計或更進一步）都會被感染。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解無人提出係密封嘅交通工具內，由交通工具的中央冷氣系統下，武漢肺炎傳染俾人？<br />\n（不過傳染程度亦由病患者/乘客坐既位置/  空調既大細/ 設施的新舊/ 巴士的新舊 影響）"},{"pid":"17d1401df5e70302b8dcc0e084f97c04bf370b9c","tid":2116324,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"要中就中，做好自己衞生意識吧"},{"pid":"a7c178ac8cd3d59f7e37b9ae0eea1f9957c80616","tid":2116324,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:30:26.000Z","msg":"科學研究係大膽假設，再細心求証。如果搵到交通工具係其中一樣傳染媒介"},{"pid":"b6adb6e6ada0e1a1cd109ea87423879a5d084226","tid":2116324,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"依家減咗班次"},{"pid":"517f395e393647538ec75535aa63fb12dc2dc0d8","tid":2116324,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6adb6e6ada0e1a1cd109ea87423879a5d084226","tid":2116324,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"依家減咗班次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"減班次對件事既影響好細"},{"pid":"a5eb1c2cbf672341ac76c04de5eb2eafa85c1773","tid":2116324,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517f395e393647538ec75535aa63fb12dc2dc0d8","tid":2116324,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6adb6e6ada0e1a1cd109ea87423879a5d084226","tid":2116324,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"依家減咗班次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T